TI  - A Comparative Study of Performance of Eigenvalue Solvers for Parallel Vector Fitting in Multiport Tabulated Data Modeling
PY  - 2023
T2  - 2023 IEEE Symposium on Electromagnetic Compatibility and Signal/Power Integrity, EMC+SIPI 2023
SP  - 306
