TI  - Verifying network performance of cyber-physical systems with multiple runtime configurations
PY  - 2015
T2  - 2015 Proceedings of the International Conference on Embedded Software, EMSOFT 2015
C7  - 7318280
SP  - 247
EP  - 255
DO  - 10.1109/EMSOFT.2015.7318280
